verbose_text: Matsumoto, et al. [XREF_BIBR] reported that Glycyrrhizae Radix, Ginseng Radix, and Zizyphi Fructus demonstrated scavenging activity for hydroxyl radical, while Scutellariae Radix, Glycyrrhizae Radix, Zingiberis Rhizoma Processum, and Coptidis Rhizoma eliminated superoxide.
